list.name: Import Failures
list.query: SELECT exception, exception_message, total_time FROM pipeline_import WHERE "success" = 'false' AND "environment" =~ /$environment$/ AND "hostname" =~ /$host$/ AND "pipeline" =~ /$pipeline$/ AND $timeFilter

list.name: InfluxDB
list.query: SELECT max("value") FROM "payment.started" WHERE ("datacenter" =~ /^America$/ AND "hostname" = 'server1') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m)
